== Short Bio
I am currently a Ph.D. student in [https://www.bme.utexas.edu/ Biomedical Engineering] working with [https://www.bme.utexas.edu/people/faculty-directory/markey Dr. Mia Markey] at [https://www.utexas.edu/ The University of Texas at Austin].
\n \n
I received my B.S. degree from the [https://physics.nju.edu.cn/ School of Physics] at [https://www.nju.edu.cn/en/main.psp Nanjing University (NJU)] in 2019. 
During my undergraduate study, I did research with Professor [https://biomech.nju.edu.cn/ Yi Cao] on single molecule biophysics, including protein-protein interactions, protein unfolding, etc. 
In summer 2018, I joined Professor [https://bioinspiredmaterials.berkeley.edu/ Phillip Messersmith]'s lab at [https://www.berkeley.edu/ University of California, Berkeley], exploring molecular design principles of lysine-DOPA wet adhesion. 
== Research Interests
- Biomedical informatics 
- Machine learning
- Biomedical image processing

